<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>What lvl is the creature that drops this weapon? I have a shaman friend that would love to have something like this. I am going to assume that since the sharkbone hammer comes from a lvl 50 creature, then this item must also come from at least a lvl 50 creatrure too. Please pose any info you can. Thanks.</font></td></tr></table>
