<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Fendar</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-10 22:09:36</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I got this weapon while hunting in Kedge Keep off the Fierce Impaler.  The Fierce spawns in the entrance room as an alternate to the the Standard Impalers. he Hits for Double 109s.  Clear the Room and he will come.</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Davien Windsor--Tunare</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-21 18:42:23</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This seems to be the rare drop now of Fierce Impaler. The commone drop being Gloomwater Harpoon.  The Fierce Impaler doesnt always come when the room is cleared.  A group must keep the room cleared to the best of its ability for quite some time before the Fierce Impaler does appear. I understand the Cloak refered to in the other comment now drops off a different Mob in Kedge.  I guess i could have gotten more for this fine weapon but I wanted a Yk and didnt want to wait.</font></td></tr></table>
