<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just a little bit more info.  We camped Kedge Keep with a Warrior, 2 Druids and a Ranger.  We were all lvl 36 40. We had to keep the room clear for a few hours before this impaler spawned.  I'm not sure what lvl but it was very high.  We healed the Tank until OOM and with the ranger Tanking with a Sharkbone Hammer we made it with a couple of Bubs of health.<BR>
luckily for me i won the roll.  Still waiting for a decent trade for it.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck for the next 1 =)<BR>
